p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;"=
>And what can David even do in this environment? He talks a lot about techn=
ology. Okay, but we don=E2=80=99t know where that gets you. Paramount isn=
=E2=80=99t getting
evicted from the club yet, but, boy, it was on the edge of the edge. And I=
=E2=80=99ve heard that, even now, <strong>Shari</strong> regrets selling. S=
he just couldn=E2=80=99t make up her mind. I think it was reality versus Fr=
eudian stuff with her father that I can=E2=80=99t address. I mean, it could=
